summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 226E, Page 16 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone approximately 0.75 acre located on the east side of 8th Avenue N.E. about 150 feet south of N.E. Northgate Way, from General Commercial (CG) Zone to Multi-Family Residental (Lowrise 3) Zone. (Petition of Don Dally, C.F. 293595).
